{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 File: app/(poems)/salvation/believe-in-god/page.mdx\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Believe in God\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Our God is greater than all things,\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 He exalts the humble and the small,\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 He brings the poor up from down low,\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 and brings the lost into the light\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 His Will is greater than that of people\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 He has knowledge of all secrets and truths\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Our God is a good God, for He shows both mercy and love\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 He is also generous, whether that be in this life or the next\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Indeed, He saves the one who calls out to Him\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 He has power to turn the evil toward the light\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 For Our God is a good God, and many are saved in death\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 He has created the Next Life, the Earth, and all things Unseen,\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 He has made some things enjoyable, even miracles\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Yet His Presence is the Ultimate Reward, our greatest hope\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 May He grant godspeed to the one who is patient,\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 May He grant glory to the one who seeks God\u8217's\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 May He grant riches to the one who seeks goodness,\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 May He grant peace to the peaceful\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 May He grant happiness to the one who seeks others,\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Praise God in all His Might, nothing dictates against Him\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
