{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Have Faith\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Who can describe faith with words?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Can any language describe it?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Faith cannot be trapped in a bottle\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Faith cannot be seen with the naked eye\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Only by what it touches and leaves behind\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Might you possibly spot its presence\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 When faith is present in a person\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Can anybody put a stop to them?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Nay, except for momentary illusions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 With faith, what is not possible for a person?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 One can heal in unexplainable ways\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 One can move the unmovable objects\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Indeed, with faith all things are possible\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Faith is found in the good decisions of people\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Faith itself is an undoubtful belief in God\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And knowing that He will do what you believe\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The one who stands firm to the very end\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 That is the one who Our Father notices\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Definitely, He will not leave that one unfulfilled\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Feelings and numbness\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Knowledge and ignorance\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 What can they do to faith?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Do they have any power?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Perhaps it is the fire or the storm\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Which desires to overcome faith\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Can even death overcome faith?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Supporting Verses\par}
