{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Be Grateful\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 There was a time when\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A certain woman came to Jesus\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 She did a beautiful thing to him\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 By pouring perfume on his head\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Appreciation and gratefulness\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They come from the heart\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Indifference shows a lack of understanding\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The scarcity of Earth, and the value of health\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 How can they be disregarded?\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Indeed, Jesus was grateful for his blessing\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Honoring her gift in front of all the others\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The righteous will be grateful as well\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 As Our Father watches in secret\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Supporting Verses\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab \u8220"\u8220"Leave her alone,\u8221"\u160 ?said Jesus.\u160 ?\u8220"Why are you bothering her? She has done a beautiful thing to me.\u160 ?The poor you will always have with you, and you can help them any time you want.\u160 ?But you will not always have me.\u160 ?She did what she could. She poured perfume on my body beforehand to prepare for my burial.\u160 ?{\i Truly I tell you, wherever the gospel is preached throughout the world,\u160 ?what she has done will also be told, in memory of her}.\u8221"\u8221" - Mark 14:6-9\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab \u8220"And he took bread, gave thanks and broke it, and gave it to them, saying, \u8220"This is my body given for you; do this in remembrance of me.\u8221"\u8221" - Luke 22:19\sa180\par}
