{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Control Yourself\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 God allows for us difficulty on Earth\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Anger problems inhibit innocent people\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Sexual desires pull people into darkness\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Poverty tests people every single day\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Yet Our Father is compassionate\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 He sees one in distress\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The one overcoming it\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Doing right and showing love\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And He rewards those extra efforts\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 So pray Him to nurture self-control\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Ask Him to gain self-discipline\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Despite the pressures of life\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Be of the moderate and calm\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Under no authority at all\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Deprive yourself to do what you must\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Every upsetting instance\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Evokes a gentle and calm response\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 One who is slow to anger\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Nurtures toleration and patience\par}
