{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Judge Righteously\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Judgement is not befitting of people\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Only Our Creator has complete knowledge\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 None can discern or comprehend likewise\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Our Father gives the same choice to all\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Both the humble and the prideful\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 That they should judge or not\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Indeed, Our Creator judges the one who judges\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Surely, like your dealings He shall deal with you\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And by His judgement He gives out mercy\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The person who judges by the surface\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 An impression, a sound, or sight\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Our Creator shall be just as harsh in return\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Rather, be of correct judgement\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And do not exercise it often\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 All of us as brothers and sisters\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Expect events to come to pass\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 For others to treat us in a certain way\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And for one thing to mean another\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 These are merely expectations\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Which may not be correct at all\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Until a conclusion must be drawn\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And a final judgement called\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Be not surprised at these times\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 When expectations are proven wrong\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Indeed, judgement is tempting by way of surety\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Supporting Verses\par}
