{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They stress not in adhering to His teaching\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 For they are not proud but forgive and are forgiven by Him\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
