{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Respect Your Family\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Our Father looks after His Children\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Those who love Him, He raises up\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 He watches on, complete in knowledge\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 So be born of self-control, be full of love\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 How tragic it is when two people\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Meant to be brothers enjoined by spirit\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Are split not by righteousness, but by sin\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Of the offensive moves, there is violence\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Driven by justifications, one directs with his hands\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Strikes and blows, not signals or signs\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Often deluded by fear, anger, envy, misled, and mistaught\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Some seek dark satisfactions, the devil\u8217's win\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 By the help of a weapon or device\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 That is a loved one given to temptation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Your Father guides you as He pleases\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 You may flee, you may scream\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Show your love for others if you stay\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Endure the affliction, speak God\u8217's Word\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Make not a threat to another\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Take no threat as a joke\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Respond not with testing, make no challenges\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Show respect, and be of the humble\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 To each person belongs their own body\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Direct your own body, direct your own house\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Honor your Father with your emotions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Anger is the gate of the ignorant\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Love is on the other side for the faithful\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 So be not angry with each other\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Each of His Children has great value\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Indeed, your mind is like a star\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Your soul cannot be exchanged for diamonds\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Our Father created each of us as the spectrum\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 One blue, one green, one red\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Be fruitful and spread seed region to region\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Associate with other peoples\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Befriend those not of your own kind\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 An authority may uphold their Law\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And parents may add discipline\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 But brothers and sisters seek not power over each other\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They reward each other often\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They seek after each others benefit\par}
