{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Speak Wisely\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Be mindful of your speech\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Words may lead people to peaceful destinations\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And they have power to destroy decades of work\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Remember what the wisest speakers do\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They hold their tongue and think carefully\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They show prudence and speak less\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Heed the guidance of Jesus Christ\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Listen to the Gospel\u8217's sayings on words of light\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 As for the petty sins\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Do not condemn them\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 For you are more alike\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 With a humble heart and foresight\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 As for the deeds of others\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Do not criticize them\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Aim for higher ways, lighter ways\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Ask questions, make suggestions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Deception is perverse speech\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Lies mislead the decision makers\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They trample on love and relations\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They create distrust between people\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Making excuses for offenses\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Leads one blindly into hateful speech\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Wise people take them lightly\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They are also mindful of people\u8217's feelings\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Give in to no pressuring speech\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 It is a friend of force, it is a foe to respect\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
