{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Use Moderation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Extremes are traps for the unwise\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Counter-productive and unreasonable\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Yet so attractive to the unaided eye\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 It\u8217's better to leave nothing overdone or underdone\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Be both mindful and moderate\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And seek what is most appropriate\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Our Father delights in those who care for each other\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 So do not seek after anything dangerous\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And surely, extremes are dangerous\par}
