{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 File: app/(poems)/worry-and-painful-thoughts/dark-feelings/page.mdx\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Dark Feelings\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Anger has snared countless people\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Indeed, the angry often feel justified\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Yet one should be far from their anger\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 For it will never serve anybody\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Yet Satan\u8217's joys are often deceiving\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 When people have a love for wealth,\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 When they celebrate the loss of an enemy,\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Or when they dwell on the unfairness of life,\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And are overcome with envy\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Truly, all of these things are abhorrent to God\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 He is concerned only with goodness and truth\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 File: app/(poems)/worry-and-painful-thoughts/peace-with-less/page.mdx\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Peace with Less\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Poverty is the bane of life\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The body may be weak\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And it may be overcome by disease\par}
