{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Haunted by horror\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Full of worry\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Indeed, poverty strikes every part\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 What do the homeless have for themselves?\par}
