{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Peaceful Thoughts\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Painful thoughts are often in conflict\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Painful thoughts are a waste and a burden\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They cycle all day long\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They haunt you for a long time\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Why change the unchangeable\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Why control the uncontrollable\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Good thoughts are accepting\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Good thoughts are hopeful\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Those people with peaceful minds\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Place their thoughts on Heaven above\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 They think of God and good things\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Sparing everyone they meet\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Do not be consumed by worry\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Don\u8217't let coming dangers frighten you\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Pessimism is grounded in delusion\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And do not be sluggish and immobile\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Be prepared and consider the science\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Treating urgently what is urgent\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And taking action for the helpless\par}
