{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Temptations\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Satan is the driver of sin\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 He seeks after its welfare\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 And he nurtures its development\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Among us are many temptations\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Within us are only more temptations\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 So be aware and pray to God\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Ask Him to spare you of temptations\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Ask Him to redirect you from evil\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 That is how you will see with light\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 So you will not be blinded and confused\par}
